dct_title_s: Fourth map, or, Map of 1692 : to accompany Willard's History of the United States
dct_description_sm: Covers the Atlantic Coast of North America from Nova Scotia to Florida. Shows route of William Penn and date of his arrival, Oct. 24, 1682. Appears in Emma Willard's History of the United States, or Republic of America, 1829 ed. Includes ill. "Massachusetts receives a new charter ... " inset map of "Places mentioned in the history of King Philip's War."
